==English==

===Interjection===
'''for God's sake'''
# An [[exclamation]] showing [[surprise]], [[impatience]], or some other emotion. 
#: '' '''For God's sake''', I didn't expect to see you here''

====Usage notes====
Sometimes though not always pluralized to ''for God's sakes'' in American usage.

There are many variants which use euphemisms for God.

